body_html: You are correct. In my effort to format them I must have copied and pasted. I will update and get someone to publish it again. Thank you. @derekhh I want to add I am really sorry about that. I know it seems crazy as how can a person copy the numbers wrong. The review process to rework the guide was so long I think I just lost focus. I will post the fresh numbers here incase you are interested and update the guide ASAP, likely this weekend but it will take a few days for someone to do the publish part.
